  * Bugfix: Timer::RepeatSetter wasn't working.

  * Bugfix: Spawning many processes in a loop
    (reported by Felix Geisendörfer)


2009.06.24, Version 0.0.6, fbe0be19ebfb422d8fa20ea5204c1713e9214d5f

